    "Lemma 7.7 (Minimal Tense Extensions and T -Completeness).",
    "For any normal modal logic L, the following are equivalent:1.",
    "L is sound and complete with respect to a class of T -BAOs; 2. the minimal tense extension L.t of L is a conservative extension of L. Fact 8.",
    "1 (1Equivalence of Fine's Semantics and Possibility Semantics).",
    "Given any Fine model M 3 (recallFigure 2.12) can be analyzed in terms of corresponding-in the precise sense of correspondence theory-bimodal interaction axioms relating [⊑] and [R]."
